{"id": 1867, "genre": 1001, "title": "当人们说“生活美学”时，你觉得他们在说什么？", "description": "这个词被滥用后，总有些有些跟“生活”无关，跟“美学”也无关的东西混在里面。你觉得他们在说啥？", "record_count": 1963, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170823173634UyCRXF7w1B02vHbf.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-24T03:00:11Z", "options": [{"id": 231170, "content": "如何优雅地花钱得到物质满足并假装得到了精神充实", "image": null, "praise_count": 482, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 231171, "content": "活着…就是为了看植物的生殖器", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 231172, "content": "瞎几把买", "image": null, "praise_count": 297, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149075}, {"id": 231428, "content": "矫情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089598}, {"id": 234244, "content": "一头栽进赚钱养家坑里的人，只有偶尔的情调与奢侈会不会是生活美学的入门呢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1126564}, {"id": 236805, "content": "就是把一些东西弄的好看一些，精致一些，然而完全不实用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200904}, {"id": 231174, "content": " 就是家居 日常用品 一定要好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930185}, {"id": 231430, "content": "没什么实用性连自己都不明白的玩意儿?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 629337}, {"id": 231175, "content": "装X", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243211}, {"id": 231431, "content": "养生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975573}, {"id": 231687, "content": "生活=过日子。美学=过得美滋滋，过得舒服 。 而两者的经济基础都是钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095310}, {"id": 231176, "content": "只是为了自我感觉良好，其实并没有什么卵用", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 77233}, {"id": 231177, "content": "用自己的生活方式教导别人怎样才能幸福\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 231178, "content": "明明就是穷，非要列举一大堆数据来证明自己买的东西性价比无懈可击", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693756}, {"id": 231179, "content": "尋求一種精神上的滿足，希望自己生活在一個美好的環境裡，尤其是在工作等其他方面都沒有辦法把握的情況下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810728}, {"id": 231180, "content": "如何让自己觉得，回家能有一种让你去商场的冲动", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889174}, {"id": 232460, "content": "过着你内心舒适，不会有各种情绪的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118898}, {"id": 231182, "content": "其实美学和生活各自都有意义，只是被某些人利用披上了促销的外衣，变成了营销的工具。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050868}, {"id": 231183, "content": "让地摊货买出旗舰店的价格。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222457}, {"id": 232465, "content": "如何优雅含蓄的装B", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052958}, {"id": 233233, "content": "享受生活", "image": "img/option/option/201709011252286yfq3Cx7JeGgFWka", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1121412}, {"id": 233745, "content": "就想看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124146}, {"id": 233746, "content": "让平凡的生活不平凡，让平凡的人生有点逼格", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124161}, {"id": 231187, "content": "关注自我，追求自己觉得美的东西比如MUji", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915794}, {"id": 231188, "content": "生活是需要美学，仪式感喝艺术感，但是好像被商业玩烂了，就没意思了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112829}, {"id": 231189, "content": "简单 舒适 人性化 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097424}, {"id": 233749, "content": "我是个木匠，出版人，设计师，摄影师，美食爱好者，旅游，文艺片巴拉巴拉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048013}, {"id": 231190, "content": "不一样的各种呈现蕴含着每一个人独一无二的标签个性以及选择", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112834}, {"id": 235800, "content": "有时候觉得炫富，有时候觉得特色", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026069}, {"id": 231193, "content": "就是好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089849}, {"id": 231194, "content": "朋友圈里p了一个小时的照骗", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313391}, {"id": 262683, "content": "再穷也要用好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250330}, {"id": 231451, "content": "再说他们有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970634}, {"id": 231197, "content": "生活美学让人心情好。我觉得挺好", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1045691}, {"id": 231198, "content": "花钱买最好的东西嘛\n（不管需不需要）", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108642}, {"id": 231199, "content": "又想骗我花钱 我怎么生活舒服你怎么知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690663}, {"id": 231200, "content": "俩字：滤镜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729051}, {"id": 231203, "content": "岁月静好……无论外界纷繁多变，我自岿然不动", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1109472}, {"id": 231204, "content": "感觉这个区域已经没法正常说话了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 77884}, {"id": 231205, "content": "在装啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112188}, {"id": 231207, "content": "极简风？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911164}, {"id": 231208, "content": "有钱就是美", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107502}, {"id": 231464, "content": "套用帕帕奈克的话:用自己没有的钱去买自己并不需要的东西，只是为了给那些其实并不在乎他们的邻居留下深刻的印象。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113904}, {"id": 231720, "content": "以钱财获得充实", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114593}, {"id": 231211, "content": "性冷淡风", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112887}, {"id": 236843, "content": "真正的生活美學，是和金錢沒有關係的，是可以在尋常生活中發現每個事物自己最美的角度。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136471}, {"id": 231212, "content": "人傻钱多的生活 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909702}, {"id": 231213, "content": "以人，个体为中心去设计生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112893}, {"id": 231726, "content": "生活都不懂的人 哪来的美", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864473}, {"id": 233006, "content": "简约带艺术气息的居家周边", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120662}]}